ly: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">万元，并具备<span lang="EN-US">1</span>年以上行业项目实施经验。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">四、招评标流程<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>1</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">、招标书发放：招标单位于<span lang="EN-US">2016</span>年<span lang="EN-US">3</span>月<span lang="EN-US">21</span>日通知投标单位前来领取招标书。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>2</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">、投标书递交：投标单位于<span lang="EN-US">2016</span>年<span lang="EN-US">3</span>月<span lang="EN-US">29</span>日 <span lang="EN-US">18:00 </span>时前，将密封好的投标书送交至深圳市福田区深南大道<span lang="EN-US">4009</span>号投资大厦<span lang="EN-US">11</span>层。（联系人：汤旭明<span lang="EN-US"> 0755-82912773 </span>）<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><span style="m