spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>5</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">、产生中标单位后，招标单位将正式通知中标单位签署有关协议，未中标单位不另行通知。对没有选中的投标人，招标人不作任何解释，也不作任何补偿，请谅解。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>6</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">、如果中标人因故放弃中标、因不可抗力提出不能履行合同，招标人可以重新确定中标人。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>7</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">、此次招标如不能满足招标单位要求，招标单位有权取消本次招标。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>8</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">、本招标文件解释权归深圳市创新投资集团有限公司所有。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 10000, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0'),
(28, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; punctuation-wrap: simple; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">3</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">月<span lang="EN-US">18</span>日至<span lang="EN-US">20</span>日，&ldquo;第十届中国（深圳）私募基金高峰论坛&rdquo;在深圳举行，论坛上发布了由私募基金大型门户网站私募排排网独家评选的私募基金相关奖项，深圳市创新投资集团（简称&ldquo;深创投&rdquo;）被评为&ldquo;<span lang="EN-US">2015</span>年中国最佳本土<span lang="EN-US">PE</span>管理机构&rdquo;。</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; punctuation-wrap: simple; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none">&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://localhost/szcx/uploadfile/2016/0418/20160418072137558.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; punctuation-wrap: simple; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">深圳市私募基金协会、私募排排网等主办了此次论坛。论坛以&ldquo;回首十年私募风云路，扬鞭十年私募新变局&rdquo;为主题，来自私募股权及私募证券投资机构、量化对冲、期货私募、期货资管、券商资管、房地产基金、<span lang="EN-US">QFII</span>及海外机构等的代表约千人参会。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; punctuation-wrap: simple; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><img alt="" src="http://localhost/szcx/uploadfile/2016/0418/20160418072302861.jpg" style="width: 460px; height: 308px;" /></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; punctuation-wrap: simple; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">深创投集团董事、财务总监刘波出席了<span lang="EN-US">20</span>日主论坛并担任&ldquo;<span lang="EN-US">PE</span>圆桌对话一：资管大时代 私募基金在变局中重构格局&rdquo;对话嘉宾。他认为当前<span lang="EN-US">VC/PE</span>行业呈现&ldquo;三多&rdquo;特点：人少钱多（关注度高）、肉少狼多（竞争激烈）、沃地戏多（京深沪杭等地项目丰富），未来<span lang="EN-US">VC/PE</span>机构业务发展将呈现&ldquo;四化&rdquo;趋势，即：多元化、专业化、国际化、投资区域集中化。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 10000, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0');
