(29, '<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: red; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">精品投后项目路演&mdash;深创投专场</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 15pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">为加强我司投后项目管理与退出，拓宽与其它投资机构、上市公司之间的合作渠道，项目管理总部（上市服务及投资企业俱乐部）推出&ldquo;精品投后项目路演&rdquo;，活动将精选一批已经获得一轮或多轮融资的优质项目进行路演。<span lang="EN-US">3</span>月<span lang="EN-US">24</span>日，&ldquo;精品投后项目路演&mdash;&mdash;深创投专场&rdquo;将火热登场。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 12pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">深圳市创新投资集团有限公司</span></b><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">主要投资中小企业、自主创新高新技术企业和新兴产业企业、初创期和成长期及转型升级企业，涵盖信息技术、互联网<span lang="EN-US">/</span>新媒体、生物医药、新能源<span lang="EN-US">/</span>节能环保、化工<span lang="EN-US">/</span>新材料、高端装备制造、消费品<span lang="EN-US">/</span>现代服务等行业领域。截至<span lang="EN-US">2016</span>年<span lang="EN-US">1</span>月底，已投资项目<span lang="EN-US">619</span>个，累计投资金额逾<span lang="EN-US">190</span>亿元，其中<span lang="EN-US">106</span>家投资企业分别在全球<span lang="EN-US">17</span>个资本市场上市。<br />\r\n<span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; </span>深创投率先建立并管理了<span lang="EN-US">73</span>支政府引导性创投基金，管理总规模近<span lang="EN-US">800</span>亿<a name="_GoBack"></a>，形成了全国性的投资和服务网络。其中深创投投资企业联谊俱乐部将持续为已投资企业提供专业的融资、上市、上下游资源整合等服务。<br />\r\n<span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; </span>路演全程将通过<b><span lang="EN-US">www.chinahtz.com</span></b>及<b><span lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span>燧石星火<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;APP</span></b>向全国的创投机构、上市公司等视频直播。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 12pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 120%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b><span style="line-height: 120%; font-family: 仿宋; color: #339966; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">一、活动概况<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 120%; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt; tab-stops: 21.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">n<span new="" style="font: 7pt " times="">&nbsp; </span></span></span><b><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">【主办】</span></b><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">深圳证券信息有限公司、深圳市创新投资集团有限公司、深圳市创业投资同业公会<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0; mso-list: l7 level1 lfo5"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">n<span new="" style="font: 7pt " times="">&nbsp; </span></span></span><b><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">【承办】</span></b><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">中国高新区科技金融信息服务平台<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-ind