及服务质量。公司<span lang="EN-US">2015</span>年营业收入达<span lang="EN-US">9500</span>万。公司曾于<span lang="EN-US">2014</span>年获得高榕资本、原腾讯集团高级执行副总裁吴宵光的天使轮融资，并于<span lang="EN-US">2015</span>年<span lang="EN-US">7</span>月完成<span lang="EN-US">A</span>轮<span lang="EN-US">3000</span>万融资。融资资金主要用于继续孵化更多区域合伙人以扩大广深业务量，完善<span lang="EN-US">IT</span>体系，同时重点拓展<span lang="EN-US">3~5</span>个其他一二线城市等。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 120%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 120%; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; vertical-align: middle; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">9.</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">路演项目：送菜哥（餐厅食材供应<span lang="EN-US">O2O</span>平台）</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; vertical-align: middle; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">【行业】移动互联网<span lang="EN-US">/</span>农业<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; vertical-align: middle; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">【项目介绍】送菜哥是餐厅食材采购<span lang="EN-US">-</span>支付<span lang="EN-US">-</span>配送<span lang="EN-US">-</span>财务的移动互联网平台。创始团队来自阿里巴巴和腾讯。送菜哥从<span lang="EN-US">2015</span>年<span lang="EN-US">4</span>月至今，专注于服务深圳餐厅市场，完成了食材采财<span lan