ly: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">日我集团投资的乐视新媒体被乐视网公司并购上市。</font></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">2014</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">年</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">6</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">月</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">5</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">日，由我司独家发起设立的红土创新基金管理有限公司（以下简称</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">&ldquo;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">红土创新基金</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">&rdquo;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">）取得中国证监会的核准设立批复。这是自新《证券投资基金法》施行以来，继证券公司、保险资产管理公司之后，国内首家获得批复的私募股权投资机构发起设立的公募基金管理公司，标志着私募资产管理机构正式进入公募基金管理行业。这为落实新基金法，拓展公募基金管理人范围，迈出了具有里程碑意义的重要一步。</font></span><br />\r\n<span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;2014</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">年</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">5</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">月</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">26</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">日，由上海证券报社主办的</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">&ldquo;2014</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">中国股权投资论坛</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">&rdquo; </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">暨第五届</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">&ldquo;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">金融资</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">&rdquo;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">奖颁奖典礼在沪举行，我司连续第五次获得</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">&ldquo;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">金融资</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">&bull;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">卓越投资机构奖</font></span><span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">&rdquo;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">。除我司外，获得该项荣誉的还有中信资本、新天域资本、君联资本、九鼎投资、达晨创投、弘毅投资、永宣创投、软银中国、启明创投等九家机构。</font></span><br />\r\n<span font-size:="" lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;2014</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">年</font></s